title: War of the Roses: Who's Hair Ties Did the Dog Swallow?
description: Missy and Sam's dog got sick and they found a bunch of hair ties in his stomach.  Missy has short hair and has for a while so she doesn't have any hair ties laying around.  Now she's wondering if Sam took the dog around another girl because the situation doesn't make sense.  Found out if he's cheating on this week's War of the Roses!
